creator: University of Bristol
descriptionHtml:
The University of Bristol Welcome app gives new students all the information they need to get started and to settle into the Bristol community.

Key features include: guides and checklists covering everything you need to do before you start and once you arrive, tailored calendar of events and activities, and how to find help and support.
descriptionShort: Everything you need to get started at University of Bristol

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Includes some minor changes to the initial on-boarding screens.

title: University of Bristol

creator: University of Bristol
descriptionHtml:
The University of Bristol app gives students the information they need to make the most of their time at Bristol.

Key features include: access to your personalised teaching timetable; helpful guides and information about your university experience; listings of extracurricular events and activities to get involved in; and how to find help and support.
descriptionShort: Everything you need to get started at University of Bristol
